  "description": "<section id=\"description\">\n<p>The words <code>before</code> and <code>after</code> are used to describe the order of events in time.</p>\n<p><code>Before</code> is used to talk about something that happens earlier than another event, and <code>after</code> is used for something that happens later. For example:</p>\n<p><code>I brush my teeth before I have breakfast</code> (Brushing teeth happens first)</p>\n<p><code>I go to work after I have breakfast</code> (Going to work happens later)</p>\n</section>",
